contents:
[[bin]]
name = "cbindgen"
path = "src/main.rs"
doc = false
required-features = [ "clap",]

[[bin]]
name = "gbindgen"
path = "src/gmain.rs"
doc = false
required-features = [ "clap", "gobject",]

[package]
name = "cbindgen"
version = "0.20.0"
authors = [ "Emilio Cobos Álvarez <emilio@crisal.io>", "Jeff Muizelaar <jmuizelaar@mozilla.com>", "Kartikaya Gupta <kats@mozilla.com>", "Ryan Hunt <rhunt@eqrion.net>",]
license = "MPL-2.0"
description = "A tool for generating C bindings to Rust code."
keywords = [ "bindings", "ffi", "code-generation",]
categories = [ "external-ffi-bindings", "development-tools::ffi",]
repository = "https://github.com/eqrion/cbindgen/"
edition = "2018"
exclude = [ "tests/profile.rs",]
default-run = "cbindgen"

[dependencies]
indexmap = "1"
log = "0.4"
serde_json = "1.0"
tempfile = "3.0"
toml = "0.5"
proc-macro2 = "1"
quote = "1"
heck = "0.3"

[dev-dependencies]
serial_test = "0.5.0"

[features]
default = [ "clap",]
gobject = []

[lib]
name = "cbindgen"
path = "src/lib.rs"

[badges.travis-ci]
repository = "eqrion/cbindgen"

[dependencies.clap]
version = "2"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.103"
default-features = false
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.syn]
version = "1.0.3"
default-features = false
features = [ "clone-impls", "extra-traits", "full", "parsing", "printing",]

[package]
name = "freerdp2"
description = "FreeRDP bindings"
homepage = "https://www.freerdp.com/"
repository = "https://github.com/elmarco/freerdp-rs"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.2.0"
license = "Apache-2.0"

[dependencies]
bitflags = "2"

[dependencies.freerdp2-sys]
version = "0.2"
path = "../freerdp2-sys"

[package]
name = "freerdp2-sys"
version = "0.2.0"
edition = "2021"
links = "freerdp-client2"
license = "Apache-2.0"
description = "FreeRDP FFI bindings"
homepage = "https://www.freerdp.com/"
repository = "https://github.com/elmarco/freerdp-rs"
build = "build.rs"

[build-dependencies]
system-deps = "7"

[package.metadata.system-deps]
freerdp2 = "2.4"
freerdp-client2 = "2.4"
winpr2 = "2.4"

[package]
name = "rdw4"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Marc-André Lureau <marcandre.lureau@redhat.com>",]
edition = "2021"

[features]
default = [ "wayland", "x11",]
bindings = []
wayland = [ "dep:wayland-protocols", "dep:gdk-wl",]
x11 = [ "dep:gdk-x11", "dep:x11",]
capi = [ "env_logger",]

[build-dependencies]
cargo_metadata = "0.19"
system-deps = "7.0"

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
derivative = "2.2.0"
libc = "0.2.155"
libloading = "0.8.3"
gl = "0.14.0"
usbredirhost = "0.4"
futures-channel = "0.3"
futures-util = "0.3"
epoxy = "0.1"

[build-dependencies.cbindgen]
path = "../cbindgen"
features = [ "gobject",]

[dependencies.khronos-egl]
version = "6.0"
features = [ "static",]

[dependencies.keycodemap]
package = "rdw-keycodemap"
path = "../keycodemap"
version = "0.1"

[dependencies.env_logger]
version = "0.11"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.wayland-protocols]
version = "0.32"
features = [ "unstable", "client",]
optional = true

[dependencies.x11]
version = "2.21"
optional = true

[dependencies.gtk]
package = "gtk4"
features = [ "unsafe-assume-initialized", "v4_12",]
version = "0.9"

[dependencies.gst]
package = "gstreamer"
version = "0.23"

[dependencies.gst-app]
package = "gstreamer-app"
version = "0.23"

[dependencies.gst-audio]
package = "gstreamer-audio"
version = "0.23"

[dependencies.gdk-wl]
package = "gdk4-wayland"
features = [ "v4_4", "egl", "wayland_crate",]
optional = true
version = "0.9"

[dependencies.gdk-x11]
package = "gdk4-x11"
features = [ "v4_4", "egl",]
optional = true
version = "0.9"

[target."cfg(unix)".dependencies]

[package.metadata.system-deps.rdw4]
version = "0.1"
feature = "bindings"

[package.metadata.capi.header]
name = "rdw"
subdirectory = "rdw4"
generation = false

[package.metadata.capi.pkg_config]
filename = "rdw4"
requires = "gtk4"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.windows]
version = "0.56.0"
features = [ "Win32_Devices_HumanInterfaceDevice", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Graphics_Gdi", "Win32_Graphics_Dxgi", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_System_Threading", "Win32_System_WindowsProgramming", "Win32_UI_Input", "Win32_UI_Input_KeyboardAndMouse", "Win32_UI_WindowsAndMessaging", "Win32_Graphics_Direct3D11",]

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.gdk-win32]
package = "gdk4-win32"
features = [ "v4_4", "win32", "egl",]
version = "0.9"

[package]
name = "rdw4-rdp"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Marc-André Lureau <marcandre.lureau@redhat.com>",]
edition = "2021"

[features]
default = []
bindings = [ "rdw/bindings",]
capi = []

[build-dependencies]
cargo_metadata = "0.19"
system-deps = "7.0"

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
derivative = "2.2.0"
futures-executor = "0.3"
futures-util = "0.3"
futures-channel = "0.3"

[build-dependencies.cbindgen]
path = "../cbindgen"
features = [ "gobject",]

[dependencies.rdw]
package = "rdw4"
path = "../rdw4"
default-features = false

[dependencies.freerdp]
package = "freerdp2"
git = "https://github.com/elmarco/freerdp-rs.git"

[dependencies.nix]
version = "0.29"
features = [ "fs", "event",]

[package.metadata.system-deps.rdw4-rdp]
version = "0.1"
feature = "bindings"

[package.metadata.capi.library]
name = "rdw4-rdp"

[package.metadata.capi.header]
name = "rdw-rdp"
subdirectory = "rdw4"
generation = false

[package.metadata.capi.pkg_config]
filename = "rdw4-rdp"
requires = [ "rdw4", "freerdp2",]

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.windows]
version = "0.60"
features = [ "Win32_System_Threading", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Security",]

[package]
name = "rdw4-spice"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Marc-André Lureau <marcandre.lureau@redhat.com>",]
edition = "2021"

[features]
default = []
bindings = [ "rdw/bindings",]
capi = []

[build-dependencies]
cargo_metadata = "0.19"
system-deps = "7.0"

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
derivative = "2.2.0"
futures-channel = "0.3"
futures-util = "0.3"

[build-dependencies.cbindgen]
path = "../cbindgen"
features = [ "gobject",]

[dependencies.rdw]
package = "rdw4"
path = "../rdw4"
default-features = false

[dependencies.spice-client-glib]
version = "0.5"

[package.metadata.system-deps.rdw4-spice]
version = "0.1"
feature = "bindings"

[package.metadata.capi.library]
name = "rdw4-spice"

[package.metadata.capi.header]
name = "rdw-spice"
subdirectory = "rdw4"
generation = false

[package.metadata.capi.pkg_config]
filename = "rdw4-spice"
requires = "rdw4"

[package]
name = "rdw4-vnc"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Marc-André Lureau <marcandre.lureau@redhat.com>",]
edition = "2021"

[features]
default = []
bindings = [ "rdw/bindings",]
capi = []

[build-dependencies]
cargo_metadata = "0.19"
system-deps = "7.0"

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
derivative = "2.2.0"

[build-dependencies.cbindgen]
path = "../cbindgen"
features = [ "gobject",]

[dependencies.rdw]
package = "rdw4"
path = "../rdw4"
default-features = false

[dependencies.gvnc]
version = "0.5"

[package.metadata.system-deps.rdw4-vnc]
version = "0.1"
feature = "bindings"

[package.metadata.capi.library]
name = "rdw4-vnc"

[package.metadata.capi.header]
name = "rdw-vnc"
subdirectory = "rdw4"
generation = false

[package.metadata.capi.pkg_config]
filename = "rdw4-vnc"
requires = "rdw4"

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://gitlab.gnome.org/malureau/rdw"]
git = "https://gitlab.gnome.org/malureau/rdw"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "bd8658f67fc6d6831565bbcbedb7a0c44d9778c0"

[source."https://github.com/elmarco/freerdp-rs"]
git = "https://github.com/elmarco/freerdp-rs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
